---
title: Caribbean Bean Chilli with Coconut Rice & Tomato Salsa
description: Red kidney beans are packed with fibre and protein, ideal to turn this mildly spiced chilli into a hearty dinner. With creamy coconut rice and a zesty tomato salsa on the side, this meal will wow you with its bold flavours.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/caribbean-bean-chilli-8a8b8885.jpg
